<PrivacyLayout appSlug="sutts" lastUpdated="2026-05-17">

  <h2>Summary</h2>
  <p>Sutts stores your smoking-log data locally on your device. Premium AI features send anonymized usage prompts to Google's Gemini API. No personal identifiers, no account, no third-party tracking.</p>

  <h2>What we collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>On-device, never uploaded:</strong> cigarettes logged, timestamps, optional notes, goals you set.</li>
    <li><strong>Sent to Google Gemini API (Premium only, opt-in):</strong> aggregated, anonymized prompts about your patterns — e.g. "user smoked 8 times today, peak at 10pm" — to generate coaching responses. Your raw log is never sent.</li>
    <li><strong>Crash reports (optional, system-level):</strong> Google Play sends anonymous crash data if you've opted in at the OS level. We do not configure any additional crash reporting.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What we don't do</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>No account creation. No email. No login.</li>
    <li>No advertising SDKs.</li>
    <li>No analytics SDKs (Firebase, Mixpanel, etc.).</li>
    <li>No selling or sharing data with third parties.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-party services</h2>
  <p>The only third-party service Sutts communicates with is Google's Gemini API, and only when Premium AI features are enabled. Gemini's data handling is governed by Google's API privacy terms.</p>

  <h2>Your rights</h2>
  <p>All your data lives in the app's local database on your device. Uninstall the app to delete it. We have nothing on a server to delete because we don't store anything on a server.</p>

  <h2>Children's privacy</h2>
  <p>Sutts is not directed at children under 13. Do not use this app if you are under 13.</p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>If this policy changes, the updated date above will change. Material changes will be flagged in the app.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions, complaints, requests: <a href="mailto:hello@brooo.app">hello@brooo.app</a></p>

</PrivacyLayout>
